snippet.title: Second Thoughts | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1998170/Second_Thoughts

Second Thoughts is a short, psychological experiment where each day you are tasked with executing someone based on the limited information provided until one person remains with their full story revealed.

Website: https://gestmorphgames.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GestmorphG
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/gestmorphgames/
